Package org.neo4j.bolt.messaging.util

Class PrimitiveLongIntKeyValueArray

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.bolt.messaging.util.PrimitiveLongIntKeyValueArray
  • public class PrimitiveLongIntKeyValueArray
extends Object
    This collection class implements a minimal map-like interface for an ordered, primitive-based key-value array. The array both maintains insertion order and ensures key values are unique.
